OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779970272
OL,3,CNew 5,000-seat Borough Park stadium
OL,4,Cplans approved
OL,6,FCouncillors have approved plans for a
OL,7,Fnew 5,000 seat stadium and adjoining
OL,8,Fsports village in Workington.
OL,10,FThe approval will see a new Borough
OL,11,FPark stadium built, to be shared by
OL,12,FWorkington Town and Workington Reds.
OL,14,FIt comes at a total cost of
OL,15,F#17,785,000.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
