PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779970272
OL,3,CNew 5,000-seat Borough Park stadium
OL,4,Cplans approved
OL,6,FThis will be financed from external
OL,7,Ffunding (71%) and Council borrowing
OL,8,F(29%), with #4.5 million funding
OL,9,Fcoming from the recently formed
OL,10,FCumbria Combined Authority - which is
OL,11,Fto include the replacement of all the
OL,12,Fterraces and increase the total
OL,13,Fcapacity at the new stadium to 5,000.
OL,15,FCumberland Council's Planning
OL,16,FCommittee signed off on phase one of
OL,17,Fthe project, which includes retail and
OL,18,Fhospitality areas including the new
OL,19,Fstands, on Wednesday 27 May.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
