FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779970272
OL,3,CNew 5,000-seat Borough Park stadium
OL,4,Cplans approved
OL,6,FLeader of Cumberland Council, Cllr
OL,7,FMark Fryer, said: "The Cumberland
OL,8,FSports Village (CSV) project presents
OL,9,Fa fantastic opportunity to create a
OL,10,Fmodern, fit-for-purpose stadium
OL,11,Ffacility for both Workington AFC and
OL,12,FWorkington Town RLFC.
OL,14,F"As well as sport, the stadium would
OL,15,Falso act as a focal point for both the
OL,16,Fcommunity and businesses within the
OL,17,Farea.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
