PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779970272
OL,3,CNew 5,000-seat Borough Park stadium
OL,4,Cplans approved
OL,6,F"An improved hospitality offer means
OL,7,Fthe stadium could also be used for
OL,8,Fmeetings, conferences, functions,
OL,9,Fevents and community activities."
OL,11,FTimeframes are being established for
OL,12,Fwhen this project could be completed,
OL,13,Fwhich marks a new chapter for the
OL,14,Ffootball and rugby league side.
OL,16,FWorkington Town was founded in 1944
OL,17,Fand started life sharing Borough Park
OL,18,Fwith Workington Reds until 1956, when
OL,19,Fthe club relocated to Derwent Park.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
