PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779970272
OL,3,CNew 5,000-seat Borough Park stadium
OL,4,Cplans approved
OL,6,FSteve Durham, the AFC's historian told
OL,7,FITV Border: "Commercially it'll be a
OL,8,Fgame changer.
OL,10,F"(Currently) the match day facilities
OL,11,Fhere are not adequate."
OL,13,FHe explained how the club will be able
OL,14,Fto host more sponsors, which represent
OL,15,F"valuable income".
OL,17,FMr Durham continued: "The new facility
OL,18,Fwill be used 7 days a week, rather
OL,19,Fthan once a fortnight like it is now."
